### ============================================================
### CareTaskController - API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task
### ============================================================

### [1] GET care tasks - today (no date param)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/tasks
X-User-Role: CNA

###

### [2] GET care tasks - specific date
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/tasks?localDate=2026-07-10
X-User-Role: NURSE

###

### [3] GET care tasks - as MANAGER
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/tasks?localDate=2026-07-10
X-User-Role: MANAGER

###

### [4] PATCH update task status - COMPLETED
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/statustasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: CNA

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "isAbnormalFlagged": false,
  "notes": "Task completed successfully"
}

###

### [5] PATCH update task status - MISSED
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/statustasks/2
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: NURSE

{
  "status": "MISSED",
  "isAbnormalFlagged": true,
  "notes": "Resident was not available"
}

###

### [6] PATCH update task status - REFUSED
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/statustasks/3
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: CNA

{
  "status": "REFUSED",
  "isAbnormalFlagged": false,
  "notes": "Resident refused bathing assistance"
}

###

### [7] PATCH update task status - back to PENDING
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/statustasks/4
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: ADMIN

{
  "status": "PENDING",
  "isAbnormalFlagged": false,
  "notes": null
}

###

### [8] FORBIDDEN - wrong role
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/tasks
X-User-Role: DON

###

### [9] UNAUTHORIZED - no role header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/care-task/tasks

###
